          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-900">3.67% – 5% (Trailing, EOD)</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-900">3.33% – 4.17% (Static)</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-slate-900">5% (Trailing, real-time)</td>
